    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed the 13-factor evaluation. Seven factors were assessed and Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was completed across five operating conditions. The simulation results fall within the experimental uncertainty band at four of five operating points. On this basis the package is accepted for submission, with the understanding that outstanding factor gaps will be addressed in a follow-on assessment cycle.",
